oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Songwriter Session - Kyshona Armstrong, David Bingaman, Jennie Hayes Kurtz, Kelsey Burkhart, Tammy Rogers King and Alex Seier - 2018-01-27
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance by participants in the acoustic guitar project including singer songwriters Kyshona Armstrong, David Bingaman and Jennie Hayes Kurtz (of Brother and the Hayes), Kelsey Burkhart, Tammy Rogers King (of the SteelDrivers) and Alex Seier. Performances from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on January 27, 2018.
